text: Andronov () is a Russian surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Aleksandr Andronov (1901–1952), Soviet physicist * Yuriy Andronov (born 1971), Russian race walker == See also == * Andronov-Pontryagin criterion of dynamical systems * Andronov (crater), a lunar crater * 11003 Andronov, a minor planet Category:Russian-language surnames
